                                                                                             NIST SP 800-53A, REV. 5                      ASSESSING SECURITY AND PRIVACY CONTROLS IN INFORMATION SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS




                                                                                             4.17 SYSTEM AND SERVICES ACQUISITION

                                                                                              SA-01           POLICY AND PROCEDURES
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SA-01_ODP[01]      personnel or roles to whom the system and services acquision policy is to be
                                                                                                                                 disseminated is/are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-01_ODP[02]      personnel or roles to whom the system and services acquision procedures are to
                                                                                                                                 be disseminated is/are deﬁned;
