                                                                                                              SA-01_ODP[03]      one or more of the following PARAMETER VALUES is/are selected: {organizaon-
                                                                                                                                 level; mission/business process-level; system-level};

                                                                                                              SA-01_ODP[04]      an oﬃcial to manage the system and services acquision policy and procedures is
                                                                                                                                 deﬁned;

