                                                                                                                                 acquision policy addresses purpose;

                                                                                                              SA-01a.01(a)[02]   the <SA-01_ODP[03] SELECTED PARAMETER VALUE(S)> system and services
                                                                                                                                 acquision policy addresses scope;

                                                                                                              SA-01a.01(a)[03]   the <SA-01_ODP[03] SELECTED PARAMETER VALUE(S)> system and services
                                                                                                                                 acquision policy addresses roles;

